    <h1 class="h4">How Butterfly Sketch Studio Works</h1>
    <p>This page documents the features I implemented for 10.3HD and how to reproduce them.</p>
    <h2 class="h6 mt-4">Advanced element: HTML5 Canvas</h2>
    <p>The Studio serializes strokes into JSON (text-only), then replays them to redraw. JSON is stored in SQLite.</p>
    <pre class="bg-light p-3 small">{"width":1000,"height":600,"title":"My Drawing","strokes":[{"tool":"pencil","color":"#156f47","size":6,"points":[{"x":10,"y":10},{"x":11,"y":15}]}]}</pre>
    <h2 class="h6 mt-4">UI/UX</h2>
    <ul><li>Bootstrap controls, toasts for saves, responsive layout.</li><li>PNG export via <code>canvas.toDataURL()</code>.</li></ul>
    <h2 class="h6 mt-4">Server & Routes</h2>
    <p>16+ routes: UI pages + JSON APIs + 404/500. See <code>index.js</code>.</p>
    <h2 class="h6 mt-4">Persistence</h2>
    <p>SQLite tables: <code>users</code>, <code>feedback</code>, <code>drawings</code>. Create with <code>createDB.js</code>.</p>
    <h2 class="h6 mt-4">Auth</h2>
    <p>Sessions + bcrypt-hashed password for admin (not plain text).</p>
